      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
