    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission. The high-revving powerplant is complemented by a fully serviced Double VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this example retains its factory-spec limited-slip differential and staggered Style 67 wheels. Mechanical sympathy is evident throughout; the rod bearing service is documented, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances. A truly turn-key enthusiast machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
