    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in a condition that can only be described as showroom-fresh, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of stone chips or swirl marks, and has been protected with a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in an immaculate state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and it has been kept in a climate-controlled environment. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and recent preventative maintenance including a full fluid flush and multi-point inspection. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist sensors, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Included in the sale are both original key fobs, all owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a turn-key opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that truly looks and drives like a new vehicle.",
